\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Pil 1.7,13\x*Nak Pol dam tebanon y…®kdat, nido Am…®n ŇäwakŇčwar…® Kab…® ji paŇčpulugok do aŇček Yesu Kristo dakon pi asat.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Kol 1.25\x*Nak gen on k…®l…® nandawit yaŇč nand…®sat, uŇčun yaŇč: PiŇčkop da ji do aŇček nak do nandaŇč yawok nam…®Ňček pi uŇčun abeŇč do nak manj…®g…®t.
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Ep 1.9-10; Kol 1.26\x*PiŇčkop da yo ag…®t dakon geni kal…®p pas…®l…® tag…®t, mani nagon paŇčalon ag…®t. UŇčun dakon geni d…®sok k…®l…® mandat.
\v 4 Ae gen on manj…®ni b…®sapmon Kristo da pi uŇčun ag…®t dakon gen pas…®l…® PiŇčkop da nol…®g…®t uŇčun dakon mib…®l…® nandani.
